{"id":"58","title":"陈丹青早期接受采访时的影像😂","type":"text","datetime":"2025-08-15T20:03:51+00:00","tags":[],"text":"陈丹青早期接受采访时的影像😂","content":"<a class=\"tgme_widget_message_reply user-color-default\" href=\"/posts/56\" \"=\"\"><blockquote><small>\n<div class=\"tgme_widget_message_author accent_color\">\n  <span class=\"tgme_widget_message_author_name\" dir=\"auto\">投机之路</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tgme_widget_message_text js-message_reply_text\" dir=\"auto\">要说全中国白手起家00后富豪榜，我现在排个前10完全没问题，可能前5都很轻松  但是我不会去参与任何媒体的这种类型的采访了。其实无论是OKX还是Binance还是好多圈内的媒体，都想采访我给我发过邀约，我想要更大的名气的话简直是再简单不过的事情，但是我全都拒绝了。因为我已经认识到了这么做会带来很多不必要的麻烦  包括你们有些人前几天看到的<i class=\"emoji\" style=\"background-image:url('/static/d5fbbc6525db1768ae3eaa79e3b22bab.png')\"><b>👀</b></i>实盘 我看到有人讨论就立马隐藏掉了，也没做任何正面回复  我现在已经过了那个爱装逼的阶段（虽然偶尔还是装一下但是我永远都只露我的一角<i class=\"emoji\" style=\"background-image:url('/static/3d1941546bc43b2a61d85cb5bb4a551e.png')\"><b>😁</b></i>）</div>\n</small></blockquote></a>陈丹青早期接受采访时的影像<i class=\"emoji\"><b>😂</b></i><a class=\"tgme_widget_message_video_player not_supported js-message_video_player\" href=\"https://t.me/journey_of_someone/58\"><i class=\"tgme_widget_message_video_thumb\" style=\"background-image:url('/static/ac2ef652e6cc2f42a10d7906ba51ab5b.jpg')\"></i>\n\n<div class=\"tgme_widget_message_video_wrap\" style=\"width:848px;padding-top:54.716981132075%\">\n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"message_video_play js-message_video_play\"></div>\n<time class=\"message_video_duration js-message_video_duration\">1:10</time>\n<div class=\"message_media_not_supported_wrap\">\n  <div class=\"message_media_not_supported\">\n    <div class=\"message_media_not_supported_label\">Media is too big</div>\n    <span class=\"message_media_view_in_telegram\">VIEW IN TELEGRAM</span>\n  </div>\n</div></a>","reactions":[{"emoji":"😁","count":"56","isPaid":false},{"emoji":"👍","count":"29","isPaid":false},{"emoji":"❤️","count":"8","isPaid":false},{"emoji":"😈","count":"4","isPaid":false},{"emoji":"💯","count":"2","isPaid":false}],"ne